Introduction:

Welcome to Crystal Radiology, your one-stop destination for advanced imaging services across four convenient locations: Harris Park Radiology Center, Granville Radiology Center, Auburn Radiology Center, and Butler Medical Imaging Radiology. Our commitment to excellence, state-of-the-art technology, and experienced professionals make us the top choice for X-Ray, Ultrasound, CT Scan, Dental CBCT, Dental X-Ray (OPG), CT Cardiac, and Injection services. Let's explore the range of services we offer and how our multiple locations benefit you.

X-Ray Services:

X-Ray imaging remains a fundamental tool in healthcare, allowing us to capture detailed images of bones, tissues, and organs. At Crystal Radiology, our X-Ray services in Harris Park, Granville, Auburn, and Butler are conducted by experienced technologists using state-of-the-art equipment, ensuring accurate and timely diagnoses for our patients.

Ultrasound Imaging:

Our ultrasound services are available at all four locations, offering real-time imaging of internal structures using sound waves. From prenatal ultrasounds to abdominal scans, our skilled sonographers provide comprehensive evaluations to aid in diagnosis and treatment planning.

CT Scan (Computed Tomography):

Crystal Radiology's CT scanning services are available at our Harris Park, Granville, and Auburn locations, offering high-resolution cross-sectional images for precise diagnoses. Whether you need a CT scan for neurological, abdominal, or cardiac assessments, our advanced technology delivers exceptional imaging results.

Dental CBCT and OPG (Orthopantomogram) X-Ray:

In addition to general radiology services, our dental imaging capabilities include Cone Beam Computed Tomography (CBCT) and Orthopantomogram (OPG) X-Rays. Patients in Harris Park, Granville, Auburn, and Butler can benefit from detailed dental assessments and treatment planning using these advanced imaging techniques.

CT Cardiac Imaging:

Our Harris Park and Auburn locations offer specialized CT cardiac imaging services, allowing for comprehensive evaluations of the heart and blood vessels. With a focus on cardiac health, we provide accurate diagnoses and valuable insights for cardiologists and referring physicians.

Injection Services:

At Crystal Radiology, we also offer injection services for contrast-enhanced imaging studies and therapeutic interventions. Patients across all locations can benefit from safe and effective injections performed by our skilled healthcare professionals.

